{"title":"交心篇","authors":["巴人"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"交心篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向党要交心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"私心化公心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公心是党性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"私心而不交，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为怕太阳明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何物藏暗室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日久不生菌？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"私心而能交，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丑恶亦晶莹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污池水出沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入溪流自清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"私心化公心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端在常交心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试看秀美者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日对明镜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公心是党性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳同光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"私心如万物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣欣各向荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交心复交心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命竞欢腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民尽一心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民尽一心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设齐猛晋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前途煊似锦。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}